OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAppeal as refugees drift on
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fboat without supplies      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UN is urging countries around the  
OL,6, Andaman Sea in South East Asia to      
OL,7, assist a boat carrying at least 150    
OL,8, Rohingya refugees which has been       
OL,9, drifting without power for two weeks.  
OL,11,FPeople on board the boat who have been 
OL,12,Fcontacted via satellite phone say a    
OL,13,Fnumber of passengers, including        
OL,14,Fchildren, have already died.           
OL,16,FThey said that food and water supplies 
OL,17,Fhad run out.                           
OL,19,FThe UN made its appeal on Friday but so
OL,20,Ffar there has been no response.        
